	Regulated Natural Gas Transportation Segment






	The Natural Gas Transportation business segment represented 24.0% and 17.3% of our total revenues during the years 2015 and 2014, respectively. Natural Gas Transportation revenues are derived mainly from firm contracts, under which pipeline capacity is reserved and paid for regardless of actual






